Who: LORD ELDER, Kup, Elita
Location: The Ark's command center

> "Maybe the situation isnt so serious as it looks"said doutbly Kup

Lord Elder nodded as he received further word from Tuscon, "You may be right."

Elder looked at his screen in front of him, "But two things still bug
me." he said as he manipulated the controls in front of him, "That
sensor ghost has been with us for quite some time. We cannot know what
it is seen. If it is Predacon or Minion it could be a spy." Elder
frowned, "and if it is, we don't know what it has seen, and what it
has communicated to its masters."

Elder started to open a channel to Nightshift, but then remembered
that he was in a communications black out, "Also I am worried about
Nightshift. The Predacons are not idiots. I wish we had spent more
time thinking this plan through. Just trapsing into the predacon
headquarters with only the predacon spark signature was probably not
the best plan." Elder tapped his fingers on the console in
frustration, "I wish we knew what was going on!"
